			<h6 class="text-header">but wait, there's more!</h6>
      But doesn't stop there - GENIUS now can be used on any site, an idea so audacious that critiques of the site include Das Racist calling it <a href="http://genius.com/Das-racist-middle-of-the-cake-lyrics/">white devil sophistry</a>. That's fucking awesome! How many other companies have been personally called out as sophists by Das Racist? And how many companies have had <a href="https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=5215884">their beef with Heroku shoot to the top of HackerNews?</a> I'll tell you the answer, in case you didn't already know - zero.
			<br>
			<br>
			In all seriousness, the International Encyclopedia of Philosophers has this to say about sophists - "The sophists were interested in particular with the role of human discourse in the shaping of reality". And what better role for GENIUS than to be at the center of the human discourse in the shaping of reality?
